{Track}<br /><strong>Talents</strong>: @Compendium[wfrp4e-core.talents.zImcTgEl2XNnbu5W]{Hardy}, @Compendium[wfrp4e-core.talents.q58lK4kULJZB5GjE]{Rover}, @Compendium[wfrp4e-core.talents.qZ4cFy6z482ZONuA]{Sturdy}, @Compendium[wfrp4e-core.talents.1dUizIgLBgn4jICC]{Strider (Any)}<br /><strong>Trappings</strong>: Bone Charms, 5 Throwing Spears, d10 Ogre Rations</p>\n<h3><strong>II. @Compendium[ogre-kingdom-wfrp4e.careers-ok.Os0YrtkcF2QRYKAY]{Ogre Hunter}</strong></h3>\n<p><strong>Status</strong>: Brass 4<br /><strong>Skills</strong>: @Compendium[wfrp4e-core.skills.MXy22hFCgntdlQrn]{Animal Care}, @Compendium[wfrp4e-core.skills.LGHozP5gmQ8cuDQV]{Athletics}, @Compendium[wfrp4e-core.skills.DRO5DLF6UcfkvNSh]{Lore (Monsters)}, @Compendium[wfrp4e-core.skills.os4NKy5Oy6sRt1eh]{Outdoor Survival}, @Compendium[wfrp4e-core.skills.OuDdJRDo3W56zk0Z]{Ranged (Crossbow)}, @Compendium[wfrp4e-core.skills.Xk5tp3aasPNtk4zt]{Stealth (Rural)}<br /><strong>Talents</strong>: &nbsp;@Compendium[wfrp4e-core.talents.XIcDsaW4D8wScezw]{Accurate Shot}, @Compendium[wfrp4e-core.talents.E3vTSCzgrasNijUO]{Fleet Footed}, @Compendium[wfrp4e-core.talents.bxbTiLzbaz4vdukT]{Hunter's Eye}, @Compendium[wfrp4e-core.talents.spdiWsONKTzkLbg3]{Stone Soup}</p>\n<p><strong>Trappings</strong>: Bone Necklace, Great Weapon</p>\n<h3><strong>III. @Compendium[ogre-kingdom-wfrp4e.careers-ok.MOA3xoDKalxLpebS]{Beast Slayer}</strong></h3>\n<p><strong>Status</strong>: Brass 5<br /><strong>Skills</strong>: @Compendium[wfrp4e-core.skills.I0yPc4PH5erWJLmu]{Intimidate}, @Compendium[wfrp4e-core.skills.cYtU0ORRFCOpQLWz]{Intuition}, @Compendium[wfrp4e-core.skills.Fs06sr7y9JKpVQmB]{Perception}, @Compendium[wfrp4e-core.skills.bVdhLdfuSAfMi3qq]{Secret Signs (Hunters)}<br /><strong>Talents</strong>: @Compendium[wfrp4e-core.talents.jLJzZb4keVvE0qRv]{Deadeye Shot}, @Compendium[wfrp4e-core.talents.8pVzgPkgWpTJvfhG]{Fearless (Monsters)}, @Compendium[wfrp4e-core.talents.uRvOg8AnCcP2ufx8]{Resolute}, @Compendium[wfrp4e-core.talents.GOtpCOZ2br14G